==English==

===Etymology===
Sanskrit for ''moon-dot''.

===Noun===
'''candrabindu''' ([[candrabindus]])

# A [[diacritic]] used in the [[Devanagari]] (ँ), [[Bengali]] (ঁ), [[Gujarati]] (ઁ), [[Oriya]] (ଁ), and [[Telugu]] (ఁ) scripts. It usually indicates that the previous vowel is nasalized.

